Duncan Lindsay for Metro.co.uk Monday 20 Feb 2017 11:13 am (Picture: BBC)

Originally, Monday 20th Februaryâ€™s visit to Walford would see Denise Fox engage in a dramatic showdown with troublesome Keegan but it has now been shifted to Tuesday as a football match is airing instead.
